Fixes issue https://github.com/CloverHealth/pytest-pgsql/issues/4 and drops support for Python 3.3.

The manual version check in `setup.py` is unfortunately necessary for versions of `pip` before 9.0, as described in [this warning](https://packaging.python.org/tutorials/distributing-packages/#python-requires) on python.org.

